Description: Simple yet extensible notification hook framework for git repositories
        ======================================================================
        
        Available backends
        ------------------
        
        -  Mail
        -  Rss
        -  IRC
        -  Jabber
        
        Requirements
        ------------
        
        pip install GitPython irc webhelpers jinja2
        
        Homepage
        --------
        
        http://renemilk.github.com/gitnotifs
        
        Usage
        -----
        
        pipe stdin to "git-notify -c some.cfg" from a post-receive hook
        
Platform: UNKNOWN
